# Export

| Mode | Requirements |
| --- | --- |
| **Image** | Current frame, chosen resolution/format (PNG), same graph/compiler as preview, download affordance |
| **Video** | Dialog: WxH, duration, FPS, bitrate, optional **full audio**; progress (**Frame N/M**), cancel, background encode (OfflineAudioContext / WebCodecs path); success → download, dismiss overlay; clamp max dims/duration |
| **WebCodecs missing** | Clear message — do not silently start |

**Refs:** `docs/user-goals/09-export.md`, `docs/user-goals/06-audio.md`.
